  schema:name "Miles O'Brien and the Persistence of Suffering" ;
  schema:description "An analysis of the 'O'Brien must suffer' pattern in Star Trek: Deep Space Nine through the Book of Job, examining faithfulness under undeserved suffering, class, and the episodic reset as theological problem." ;
